  // Capture The Flag - CTF
  "CaptureTheFlag": "CAPTURE THE FLAG",
  "ModeCaptureTheFlag": "Gamemode: Capture The Flag",
  "ModeDescribe.CaptureTheFlag": "In the Capture The Flag gamemode, there are two teams: Yellow and Blue. Each team has a flag in their base. The goal is to capture the enemy's flag and bring it back to your base. The first team to do so wins!\\nPlayers can be tagged by the enemy team, which will send them back to their base or kill them, depending on the settings. Players who are carrying a flag cannot tag other players.\\n\\nYou can grab the flag by clicking your <b>Vanish</b> button near it.",
  "GameModeTutorial.CaptureTheFlag": "<size=90%>The current game mode is <#1313c2>Capture The Flag</color>.</size>\\n<size=80%>Get to the base of the enemy team and press Vanish to pick up their flag.\\nBring it back to your own base for your team to win.\\nPress Kill on someone to tag them, this will get rid of that player temporarily or permanently.</size>",
  "CTF_AlertTeamMembersOfEnemyFlagTaken": "Alert Team Members When the Enemy's Flag is Taken",
  "CTF_AlertTeamMembersOfFlagTaken": "Alert Team Members When their Flag is Taken",
