  // Deathrace
  "Deathrace": "DEATHRACE",
  "ModeDeathrace": "Gamemode: Deathrace",
  "ModeDescribe.Deathrace": "In the Deathrace gamemode, there is a specific track you need to follow on the map, repeatedly. If you enter a room that isn't the next one on the track, you die! You must complete all laps first to win.\\n\\nSome power-ups are available next to the track, go near them to pick them up. It will tell you what they do and how to use them when you pick them up. You can store multiple power-ups and use them one at a time.",
  "Deathrace.Tutorial.Basics": "The current game mode is <#AFAFAF>Deathrace</color>.\\n<size=90%>There's a specific track you need to follow on this map, repeatedly.\\nIf you enter a room that isn't the next one on the track, you die!\\nYou must complete all laps first to win.",
  "Deathrace.Tutorial.PowerUps": "Some power-ups are available next to the track,\\ngo near them to pick them up.\\nIt will tell you what they do\\nand how to use them when you pick them up.",
  "Deathrace.Tutorial.Track": "Track:\\n{0}",
  "Deathrace.ClockwiseOption": "Toggle this to reverse the track direction",
