  // Quiz
  "Quiz": "QUIZ",
  "ModeQuiz": "Gamemode: Quiz",
  "ModeDescribe.Quiz": "In the Quiz game mode, you must answer questions correctly to survive. There are various difficulties with varying time limits. Each question has 5 answer choices: A, B, C, D, E. Each choice has a room name next to the answer. To pick an answer, you must enter the room corresponding to the answer. If you answer correctly, you survive. If you don't answer enough questions correctly, you eventually die or compete in a Free For All (FFA) match with the other players who got the questions wrong.",
  "Quiz.Tutorial.Basics": "The current game mode is <#CF2472>Quiz</color>.\\n<size=90%>You'll get questions, each with 5 choices: A, B, C, D, E.\\nYou must answer the questions correctly within the time limit\\nby entering the room corresponding to the correct answer.\\nThe rooms on this map are:\\n{0}</size>",
  "Quiz.Tutorial.OnCorrectAnswer": "<size=90%>If you answer <#00ff00>correctly</color>, you get to survive.</size>",
  "Quiz.Tutorial.OnWrongAnswer": "<size=90%>If you answer <#ff0000>incorrectly</color>, you will most likely die.</size>",
  "Quiz.Tutorial.TestRound": "<size=90%>We'll play a test round to show you how it works.</size>",
