  "ComboUsage": "\n<b><u>Usage Format:</u></b>\n/combo {add/ban/remove/allow} {main role} {addon} [all]\n\n<size=60%>By default, the combo is added to the current preset. If you want it to be added for all presets, type 'all' at the end.\nExample: /combo add Niceguesser Doubleshot all</size>",
