  "DraftStart": "Drafting has started! You now have a chance to pick a role from the list below if you'd like to get one of them for the next game. The roles you get to choose from are:\\n\\n{0}\\n\\nChat commands to use:\\n- Pick role: <b>/draft [number]</b>\\n- View description of role: <b>/dd [number]</b>\\nReplace [number] with the number of the role you want to pick. Example: <b>/draft 4</b>\\n<size=70%>If you don't pick a role, you get a random one like you normally would.</size>",
